    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi everyone! \ud83c\udf1f I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered its whole life, kept tucked away in a garage, and has been meticulously cared for. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that's basically flawless, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed! \ud83d\ude0a",
      "price": 43900.0,
