    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true showroom-quality specimen that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, with its original factory paint retaining a deep, mirror-like luster free of any chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in absolute pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of wear or creasing, and every button and electronic component functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive folder of authorized service records and a recent multi-point inspection. From the untouched alloy wheels to the spotless engine bay, this is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning enthusiast to own a benchmark example of this model. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
